        <h4>Detailed Overview of IV Drip Therapy</h4>
        <p>
          IV drip therapy delivers fluids, vitamins, minerals, and medications directly into the
          bloodstream, ensuring near‑100% absorption compared to oral supplements. This allows for
          immediate effects, precise dosing, and improved efficacy.
        </p>
        <p>
          Common nutrients include electrolytes (sodium, potassium), vitamins (C, B‑complex),
          minerals (magnesium, zinc), and amino acids for targeted wellness goals. Types of IV
          therapy range from hydration and energy drips to immunity boosters, beauty formulations,
          and anti‑aging therapies.
        </p>

        <h4>Reasons for Increasing Popularity in Dubai</h4>
        <ul>
          <li><b>Convenience</b> – Fits busy schedules without clinic visits.</li>
          <li><b>Privacy</b> – Favored by professionals and public figures for discretion.</li>
          <li>
